<p class="h1">SERUG</p>
<p class="fl">Reu’s son from Shem’s line (<a href="?bref=Gen.11.20-23">Gn 11:20-23</a>), Abraham’s forefather and an ancestor of Jesus Christ (<a href="?bref=Luke.3.35">Lk 3:35</a>; <span class="sc">kjv</span> “Saruch”). <span class="ital">See</span> <a href="?item=GenealogyofJesusChrist_Article_TyndaleOpenBibleDictionary">Genealogy of Jesus Christ</a>.</p>
